snippet.title: SMG2: Collectors Anxiety 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
~~~~~Information~~~~~

Welcome to the 2023 trailer video of Super Mario Galaxy 2: Collectors Anxiety! This last year was pretty rough, finished a voluntary work year and started a real job lately so there wasn't much time to work on the mod. Also motivation was on an all-time low, but I hope you still enjoy this little progress update in form of a new Trailer.

~~~~~~~~~~
This Hack is all about collecting. It's a rather chill hack to play when you just wanna calm down. 
-------------------------
If you have any questions, ideas or suggestions, join the Collectors Anxiety Discord Server: https://discord.gg/FW6XFcPjPr
~~~~~~~~~~

~~~~~Download Link~~~~~

Collectors Anxiety Demo-Download:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jLN5cvEflmw

~~~~~Music used in the Trailer~~~~~

Galaxy Colloseum from Mario Kart Wii
Sunahara Desert from Fast Racing Neo
Ninji Jump Party from Super Mario Bros. Wonder

#collectorsanxiety #supermariogalaxy2
